## 2. 链式栈（基于链表）

**核心思想**：使用**单链表**，表头作为栈顶。  
`push` → 头插法；`pop` → 删除头结点。

### 图解

```
push(3):
head → [3] → [2] → [1] → null

pop():
head → [2] → [1] → null （返回 3）
```

### 代码实现

**C++ 链式栈**
```cpp
template <typename T>
class LinkedStack {
    struct Node {
        T data;
        Node* next;
        Node(const T& val, Node* nxt = nullptr) : data(val), next(nxt) {}
    };
    Node* head = nullptr;
    int cnt = 0;

public:
    void push(const T& val) {
        head = new Node(val, head);
        ++cnt;
    }
    void pop() {
        if (!head) throw std::underflow_error("Stack underflow");
        Node* tmp = head;
        head = head->next;
        delete tmp;
        --cnt;
    }
    T top() const {
        if (!head) throw std::underflow_error("Stack is empty");
        return head->data;
    }
    bool empty() const { return head == nullptr; }
    int size() const { return cnt; }

    ~LinkedStack() {
        while (head) {
            Node* tmp = head;
            head = head->next;
            delete tmp;
        }
    }
};
```

**C# 链式栈**
```csharp
public class LinkedStack<T>
{
    private class Node
    {
        public T Data;
        public Node Next;
        public Node(T data, Node next) { Data = data; Next = next; }
    }
    private Node head;
    private int count;

    public void Push(T item)
    {
        head = new Node(item, head);
        count++;
    }
    public T Pop()
    {
        if (head == null) throw new InvalidOperationException("Stack empty");
        T result = head.Data;
        head = head.Next;
        count--;
        return result;
    }
    public T Peek()
    {
        if (head == null) throw new InvalidOperationException("Stack empty");
        return head.Data;
    }
    public bool IsEmpty => head == null;
    public int Count => count;
}
```

## 3. 顺序栈 vs. 链式栈

| 维度 | 顺序栈 (数组) | 链式栈 (链表) |
|------|---------------|---------------|
| 内存空间 | 连续，可能有扩容消耗 | 不连续，每个节点有指针开销 |
| 操作复杂度 | 均为 O(1) | 均为 O(1) |
| 是否易实现 | 简单 | 简单，但需注意内存释放 |
| 考试常见陷阱 | 忘写扩容逻辑 | 忘写析构/判空 |

